B.VG=s([B.KQ,B.Lj,B.KL],t.l)
B.T_=new A.V(B.ak,"Ba\u011flamda \xd6rnekler",null,B.VG,null,null)
B.Q7=new A.V(B.al,"\u2708\ufe0f S\u0131nav \u0130pucu",'Kelime sorular\u0131 \xe7o\u011funlukla **e\u015f anlaml\u0131** sorar. Yayg\u0131n tuzaklar:\n\u2022 "nacelle" \u2260 "fuselage" (nacelle motor kovan\u0131d\u0131r)\n\u2022 "aileron" **roll** (yuvarlama) eksenini kontrol eder, yaw de\u011fil\n\u2022 "elevator" **pitch** (yunuslama) eksenini kontrol eder, roll de\u011fil\n\nEzber form\xfcl\xfc: **A**ileron \u2192 **A**ks (roll), **E**levator \u2192 **E**levasyonu (pitch), **R**udder \u2192 **R**otasyon (yaw).',null,null,null)
