B.RS=new A.V(B.al,"\u2708\ufe0f Okuma Stratejisi",'ATIS t\xfcr\xfc okuma sorular\u0131 i\xe7in:\n\u2022 **ATIS harfi** her 30-60 dakikada de\u011fi\u015fir \u2014 sorular "Bravo ne anlama gelir?" diye sorabilir\n\u2022 **Kullan\u0131lan pist** var\u0131\u015flar ve kalk\u0131\u015flar i\xe7in farkl\u0131 olabilir\n\u2022 **Ge\xe7i\u015f seviyesi** = ge\xe7i\u015f irtifas\u0131n\u0131n \xfczerindeki en d\xfc\u015f\xfck kullan\u0131labilir u\xe7u\u015f seviyesi\n\u2022 Sondaki **\xf6zel bildirimler** \xe7o\u011funlukla s\u0131nanan ayr\u0131nt\u0131y\u0131 i\xe7erir\n\u2022 Sorular genellikle "ATIS\'e g\xf6re \u2026 i\xe7in hangi pist kullan\u0131labilir?" diye sorar',null,null,null)
