B.SO=new A.V(B.al,"\u2708\ufe0f S\u0131nav \u0130pucu",'\xdcnl\xfc **seslerden** \xf6nce "a" de\u011fil "an" kullan\u0131n \u2014 yaln\u0131zca \xfcnl\xfc harflerden de\u011fil:\n\u2022 **an** ILS approach (I = \xfcnl\xfc ses)\n\u2022 **an** RNAV procedure (R = \xfcns\xfcz harf, ama "RNAV" "ar" \xfcnl\xfc sesiyle ba\u015flar)\n\u2022 **a** NOTAM (N = \xfcns\xfcz ses)\n\u2022 **a** VOR (V = \xfcns\xfcz ses)\n\nGenel ba\u011flamda havac\u0131l\u0131k sistemleriyle s\u0131f\u0131r artikel:\n\u2713 "Hydraulic systems are used in..." ("The hydraulic systems" de\u011fil)\n\u2713 "ILS provides guidance" ("The ILS provides" de\u011fil)',null,null,null)
