B.QU=new A.V(B.aj,"\u0130leri kelime bilgisi iyiyi m\xfckemmelden ay\u0131r\u0131r","ICAO Seviye 5 ve 6 yeterli\u011fi, az kullan\u0131lan ancak y\xfcksek \xf6neme sahip teknik s\xf6zc\xfcklere hakim olmay\u0131 gerektirir. Bu ders, ileri d\xfczey adaylar\u0131 ay\u0131rt eden ve en zor s\u0131nav sorular\u0131nda s\u0131k\xe7a kar\u015f\u0131la\u015f\u0131lan terimleri kapsar.",null,null,null)
B.Sk=new A.V(B.B,"\ud83c\udfc6 \u0130leri Operasyonel Terimler","**EDTO/ETOPS** \u2014 Extended Diversion Time Operations (flying far from alternate airports)\n**RVSM** \u2014 Reduced Vertical Separation Minima (300m / 1,000ft between FL290\u2013FL410)\n**PBN** \u2014 Performance-Based Navigation (RNP, RNAV specs)\n**MNPS** \u2014 Minimum Navigation Performance Specification (oceanic)\n**MEL** \u2014 Minimum Equipment List (approved deferred defects)\n**CDL** \u2014 Configuration Deviation List (approved structural deviations)\n**AOG** \u2014 Aircraft on Ground (urgent unserviceable aircraft)",null,null,null)
B.SG=new A.V(B.B,"\u26a0\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik Kritik Kelime Bilgisi","**Controlled flight into terrain (CFIT)** \u2014 aircraft in controlled flight strikes terrain\n**Loss of control in-flight (LOC-I)** \u2014 most fatal accident category\n**Runway incursion** \u2014 unauthorized presence on runway\n**Airspace infringement** \u2014 entering controlled airspace without clearance\n**Human factors** \u2014 study of human performance in aviation systems\n**Crew Resource Management (CRM)** \u2014 effective use of all resources\n**Threat and Error Management (TEM)** \u2014 proactive safety model",null,null,null)
B.LD=new A.aJ("The accident was classified as CFIT \u2014 the crew was unaware of the proximity to terrain.","Kaza, CFIT olarak s\u0131n\u0131fland\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131 \u2014 ekip, araziye olan yak\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan habersizdi.","CFIT")
B.Ly=new A.aJ("Under RVSM, vertical separation between FL290 and FL410 is reduced to 1,000 feet.","RVSM kapsam\u0131nda, FL290 ile FL410 aras\u0131ndaki dikey ay\u0131rma 1.000 fite indirilmi\u015ftir.","RVSM")
B.Lb=new A.aJ("The aircraft was dispatched on the MEL, with one hydraulic pump deferred.","U\xe7ak, bir hidrolik pompa ertelenmi\u015f olarak MEL'e g\xf6re hava arac\u0131 olarak g\xf6nderildi.","MEL")
