B.Uj=s(["Both are turned ON","One is ON and one is OFF","Both are turned OFF","The position does not matter"],t.s)
B.a4H=new A.ad(-101,B.az,607,"During wet motoring, what is the position of the ignition systems?",B.Uj,2,B.P,null,null,null)
B.VW=s(["Engine speed only","The starter motor temperature","The exhaust nozzle for signs of fuel","The HP rotor vibration"],t.s)
