B.VX=s([B.a5f,B.a4H,B.a4j],t.C)
B.Qh=new A.V(B.ad,"Pratik Sorular",'"Wet motoring the engine is necessary to test the fuel system. When an engine is wet motored, the two ignition systems are turned OFF and the starter is engaged to turn the HP rotor to 15%-20% N2. At N2 = 15%, the HP fuel shutoff valve control lever is moved to ON and the engine exhaust nozzle is carefully monitored for any sign of fuel."',null,null,B.VX)
